olavina aasare ( kannada : ಒಲವಿನ ಆಸರೆ ) is a 1988 indian kannada language film directed and produced by k. v. jayaram . the film starred vishnuvardhan , rupini and sudha chandran in the lead roles . the music was composed by m. ranga rao , and the dialogues and lyrics were written by kunigal vasanth and doddarangegowda , respectively . the film is based on a novel with the same title written by tanuja . the film was declared a musical hit at the box office upon its release .